<document>
  
  <header>
    <title>Nutch Mailing Lists</title>
  </header>
  
  <body>
  
    <section>
      <title>Users</title>

      <p>If you use Nutch, please subscribe to the Nutch user mailing list.</p>

      <p>
        The Nutch user mailing list is :
        <a href="mailto:nutch-user@lucene.apache.org">nutch-user@lucene.apache.org</a>.
      </p>      
      <ul>
        <li><a href="mailto:nutch-user-subscribe@lucene.apache.org">Subscribe to List</a></li>
        <li><a href="mailto:nutch-user-unsubscribe@lucene.apache.org">Unsubscribe from List</a></li>
        <li><a href="http://www.mail-archive.com/nutch-user%40lucene.apache.org/">Search List Archive</a></li>
        <li><a href="http://lucene.apache.org/mail/nutch-user/">View List Archive</a></li>
      </ul>
      <note>In order to post to the list, it is necessary to first subscribe to it.</note>
    </section>
  
    <section>
      <title>Developers</title>

      <p>If you'd like to contribute to Nutch, please subscribe to the
      Nutch developer mailing list.</p>

      <p>
        The Nutch developer mailing list is :
        <a href="mailto:nutch-dev@lucene.apache.org">nutch-dev@lucene.apache.org</a>.
      </p>      
      <ul>
        <li><a href="mailto:nutch-dev-subscribe@lucene.apache.org">Subscribe to List</a></li>
        <li><a href="mailto:nutch-dev-unsubscribe@lucene.apache.org">Unsubscribe from List</a></li>
        <li><a href="http://www.mail-archive.com/nutch-dev%40lucene.apache.org/">Search List Archive</a></li>
        <li><a href="http://lucene.apache.org/mail/nutch-dev/">View List Archive</a></li>
      </ul>
      <note>In order to post to the list, it is necessary to first subscribe to it.</note>
    </section>
  
    <section>
      <title>Commits</title>

      <p>If you'd like to see changes made in Nutch's <a
      href="version_control.html">version control system</a>
      then subscribe to the Nutch commit mailing list.</p>

      <ul>
        <li><a href="mailto:nutch-commits-subscribe@lucene.apache.org">Subscribe to List</a></li>
        <li><a href="mailto:nutch-commits-unsubscribe@lucene.apache.org">Unsubscribe from List</a></li>
        <li><a href="http://www.mail-archive.com/nutch-commits%40lucene.apache.org/">Search List Archive</a></li>
        <li><a href="http://lucene.apache.org/mail/nutch-commits/">View List Archive</a></li>
      </ul>
    </section>
  
    <section>
      <title>Agents</title>

      <p>If you use Nutch to perform extensive crawls of sites that
      you do not control, please subscribe to the Nutch agent mailing
      list.  This is where we encourage webmasters to post questions
      about the Nutch crawler.</p>

      <p>
        The Nutch agent mailing list is :
        <a href="mailto:nutch-agent@lucene.apache.org">nutch-agent@lucene.apache.org</a>.
      </p>      
      <ul>
        <li><a href="mailto:nutch-agent-subscribe@lucene.apache.org">Subscribe to List</a></li>
        <li><a href="mailto:nutch-agent-unsubscribe@lucene.apache.org">Unsubscribe from List</a></li>
        <li><a href="http://www.mail-archive.com/nutch-agent%40lucene.apache.org/">Search List Archive</a></li>
        <li><a href="http://lucene.apache.org/mail/nutch-agent/">View List Archive</a></li>
      </ul>

    </section>
  
    
  </body>
  
